{"tid":1792743,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【正視聽】會員#30209「我要裸跑」涉嫌散播不實資訊，誣衊港大教授陳祖為","createTime":"2019-12-22T01:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T08:17:30.000Z","uid":138409,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1ce8352e5e9e58ad1432a4c31835497c8d113324","tid":1792743,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T01:24:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">會員：我要裸跑<br />\n編號：#30209</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">原post：</span><br />\n［報料］學者葉健民、陳祖為與林鄭密室談判：以檢討委員會取代調查委員會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1791710\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1791710</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mis2TJb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmis2TJb.png&h=d03d3ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">事實：</span><br />\n1）會員「我要裸跑」引用王慧麟篇專欄，文中並無指明任何人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/column/新聞/不忍人之心-201018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%8D%E4%BA%BA%E4%B9%8B%E5%BF%83-201018&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3M5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=e3d39d9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/column/新聞/不忍人之心-201018</a><br />\n對葉健民、陳祖為等人指控，純屬道聽塗說，目前未提出任何確實證據<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wcJUKW8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwcJUKW8.png&h=e144a504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2）陳祖為教授已澄清，一直支持成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Chanchowaijoseph/posts/10159229223205550\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FChanchowaijoseph%2Fposts%2F10159229223205550&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3M5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=385f528e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Chanchowaijoseph/posts/10159229223205550</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cC1bGDC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcC1bGDC.png&h=07e6351f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦有媒體佐證，佢早至6月12號已經支持成立調查委員會<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3017781/hong-kong-protests-pro-beijing-camp-squabbles-former-chief\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2F3017781%2Fhong-kong-protests-pro-beijing-camp-squabbles-former-chief&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3M5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=7b288bd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3017781/hong-kong-protests-pro-beijing-camp-squabbles-former-chief</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5hSeEy4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5hSeEy4.jpg&h=6149c159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於一直用陳祖為成立民主思路、鬧佢同湯家驊一樣嘅人<br />\n<blockquote>事隔一個多星期，陳祖為打破沉默，解釋退出的原因是與民主思路召集人湯家驊實踐溫和路線手法上的不同，「我覺得他太針對民主派人士的言行、質疑對方背後的動機、評價他們的誠信和智慧度&hellip;&hellip;這不但無助溫和路線推行，有少少增加怨恨和對立」。他又指出，湯近月的言論令人覺得「很親建制」，但他強調並非因為湯加入行會而退出民主思路。</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20170816/s00002/1502819463897/%E9%99%B3%E7%A5%96%E7%82%BA-%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A%E5%A4%AA%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE-%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF-%E6%8C%87%E6%B9%AF%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E7%84%A1%E5%8A%A9%E6%BA%AB%E5%92%8C%E8%B7%AF%E7%B7%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170816%2Fs00002%2F1502819463897%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E7%25A5%2596%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%25A9%258A%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E9%2587%259D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE-%25E9%2580%2580%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%2580%259D%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E8%25A8%2580%25E8%25AB%2596%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%258A%25A9%25E6%25BA%25AB%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E7%25B7%259A&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3M5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=2d8673e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170816%2Fs00002%2F1502819463897%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E7%25A5%2596%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%25A9%258A%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E9%2587%259D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE-%25E9%2580%2580%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%2580%259D%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E8%25A8%2580%25E8%25AB%2596%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%258A%25A9%25E6%25BA%25AB%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E7%25B7%259A&h=e66db3d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20170816/s00002/1502819463897/%E9%99%B3%E7%A5%96%E7%82%BA-%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A%E5%A4%AA%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE-%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF-%E6%8C%87%E6%B9%AF%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E7%84%A1%E5%8A%A9%E6%BA%AB%E5%92%8C%E8%B7%AF%E7%B7%9A</a><br />\n<br />\n更加唔好講陳祖為教授一直以來都係溫和派，但依家都響度反思武力抗爭嘅可行性（及其限制）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/radio/radio1/programme/university_knowledge_platform/episode/607746\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Fradio%2Fradio1%2Fprogramme%2Funiversity_knowledge_platform%2Fepisode%2F607746&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3M5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=af3068ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/radio/radio1/programme/university_knowledge_platform/episode/607746</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「我要裸跑」被質疑嘅時候<br />\n至今一直拒絕撤回言論，更聲稱<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8vT19oa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8vT19oa.png&h=7759f710&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n指控嘅舉證責任應該落於控方身上<br />\n更何況依家被指控嘅係和理非手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「我要裸跑」你收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"2ecb293200c29b5cd45d5afa3b20c93e67318389","tid":1792743,"uid":138409,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T01:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ojk74WM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOjk74WM.jpg&h=eb1d04ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04e5f9f28f28470a85ed94cd60ff04a8ceb83aea","tid":1792743,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T01:25:10.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce57d1ebcf4117ceed5010e85a689130bf97919b","tid":1792743,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T01:29:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"556367219ccfd99cacd8d9846b8a3c0d461737ea","tid":1792743,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T01:29:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5fdb02953d031a9512df9098b9a305d4d70a500","tid":1792743,"uid":138409,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T01:29:26.000Z","msg":"此人已改名為<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港大阮民安</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/30209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/30209</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你改名都無撚用啊屌你分化狗"},{"pid":"473759962607a243c83b985aa45627f1362392fe","tid":1792743,"uid":214214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5fdb02953d031a9512df9098b9a305d4d70a500","tid":1792743,"uid":138409,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T01:29:26.000Z","msg":"此人已改名為<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港大阮民安</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/30209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/30209</a><br />\n<br />